---
title: Warm Goat's Cheese and Apple Salad with crostini and caramelised onion chutney
description: Crispy ciabatta is the perfect pairing for the warm honeyed goat's cheese and the sweet but slightly tart chutney that make up this surprisingly exciting salad.
